         <article id="post-712" class="post-712 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-uncategorized tag-windows-10 tag-95"> 
          <img width="750" height="410" src="http://blog-qiniu.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-17-15-750x410.png" class="single-featured wp-post-image" alt="" /> 
          <div class="post-inner-content"> 
           <header class="entry-header page-header"> 
            <h1 class="entry-title ">windows 10 上手体验：简洁高速</h1> 
            <div class="entry-meta"> 
             <span class="posted-on"><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> <a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/712" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-06-18T10:34:06+00:00">2015年6月18日</time></a></span>
             <span class="byline"> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://blog.lxx1.com/author/admin">科技爱好者</a></span></span> 
             <span class="cat-links"><i class="fa fa-folder-open-o"></i> <a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/topics/uncategorized" rel="category tag">默认分类</a> </span> 热度：283℃ 
            </div>
            <!-- .entry-meta --> 
           </header>
           <!-- .entry-header --> 
           <div class="entry-content"> 
            <p>昨天在电脑上安装了windows 10，使用了一段时间，感觉windows 10确实很强大，微软做了很大的改变，用户体验也变得非常好。</p> 
            <p class="entry-title ">首先是在安装、升级上，windows 10&nbsp;可以不用重新安装，只要在windows 10推出后点击升级即可，大大降低了升级难度，使得普通用户也可以方便、快速的升级。windows 10 安装请看这里：<a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/694" target="_blank">windows 10 安装体验。</a></p> 
            <p class="entry-title "><span id="more-712"></span></p> 
            <p>其次是在系统功能上的改变，在windows 10中，用户熟悉的开始菜单回归了，并且将 Metro应用加入到开始菜单中，取消了 Metro桌面，再也不用切换桌面啦，可以自己在设置中选择桌面模式。</p> 
            <figure id="attachment_713" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 1376px">
             <a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-29-30.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-713" src="http://blog-qiniu.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-29-30.png" alt="全新的开始菜单" width="1366" height="768" srcset="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-29-30.png 1366w, http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-29-30-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></a>
             <figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text">
              全新的开始菜单
             </figcaption>
            </figure> 
            <p>windows 10&nbsp;加入Cortana（小娜）的智能语音助手，点击搜索，稍等片刻在搜索框的右侧多出一个麦克风按钮，点击它后就可以和“小娜”进行交流了。当然，暂时跟小娜还只能用英语交流。当你说完“Hey, Cortana”后，不需要等待即可直接继续进行交流了。</p> 
            <figure id="attachment_714" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 1376px">
             <a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-38-23.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-714" src="http://blog-qiniu.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-38-23.png" alt="Cortana（小娜）智能语音助手" width="1366" height="768" srcset="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-38-23.png 1366w, http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-38-23-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></a>
             <figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text">
              Cortana（小娜）智能语音助手
             </figcaption>
            </figure> 
            <p>windows 10&nbsp;还有许多的应用程序发生了变化，变得更快、体验更好。比如全新的浏览器、可以放大缩小的metro应用以及新家入的通知中心。</p> 
            <p><a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-43-06.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716" src="http://blog-qiniu.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-43-06.png" alt="Windows 10-2015-06-18-00-43-06" width="1366" height="768" srcset="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-43-06.png 1366w, http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-00-43-06-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></a></p> 
            <figure id="attachment_718" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 1376px">
             <a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-09-25.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-718" src="http://blog-qiniu.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-09-25.png" alt="天气应用" width="1366" height="768" srcset="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-09-25.png 1366w, http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-09-25-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></a>
             <figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text">
              天气应用
             </figcaption>
            </figure> 
            <figure id="attachment_719" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 1376px">
             <a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-11-24.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-719" src="http://blog-qiniu.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-11-24.png" alt="应用中心" width="1366" height="768" srcset="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-11-24.png 1366w, http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-11-24-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></a>
             <figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text">
              应用中心
             </figcaption>
            </figure> 
            <p><a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-12-10.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-720" src="http://blog-qiniu.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-12-10.png" alt="Windows 10-2015-06-18-01-12-10" width="1366" height="768" srcset="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-12-10.png 1366w, http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-12-10-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></a></p> 
            <figure id="attachment_721" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 1376px">
             <a href="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-16-58.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-721" src="http://blog-qiniu.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-16-58.png" alt="新加入的通知中心" width="1366" height="768" srcset="http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-16-58.png 1366w, http://blog.lxx1.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Windows-10-2015-06-18-01-16-58-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></a>
             <figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text">
              新加入的通知中心
             </figcaption>
            </figure> 
            <p>&nbsp;</p> 
            <p>不得不说，windows 10的改变很大，用户的体验大大提高，并且按照微软的说法，windows 10可快速启动、快速恢复，并且附带比以往过更多的安全功能，同时，windows 10上的应用启动速度大大加快，就让我们一起期待正式版的到来。</p> 
            <p>&nbsp;</p> 
            <p>更多体验图片请戳这里：</p> 
            <p><a href="http://lxx1.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=411&amp;fromuid=766" target="_blank">windows 10 全新体验</a><br /> http://lxx1.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=411&amp;fromuid=766</p> 
            <hr /> 
